Пример JavaScript-кода для модели:

```
class Calculator {
  calculateMonthlyPayment(amount, rate, term) {
    const monthlyRate = rate / 1200;
    const monthlyPayment = amount * monthlyRate / (1 - (1 / Math.pow(1 + monthlyRate, term)));
    return monthlyPayment;
  }

  calculateTotalAmount(amount, rate, term) {
    const monthlyPayment = this.calculateMonthlyPayment(amount, rate, term);
    const totalAmount = monthlyPayment * term;
    return totalAmount;
  }
}
```

Пример JavaScript-кода для презентера:

```
class CalculatorPresenter {
  constructor(view, model) {
    this.view = view;
    this.model = model;
    this.view.bindSubmit(this.onSubmit.bind(this));
    this.view.bindInput(this.onInput.bind(this));
  }

  onSubmit() {
    const amount = parseFloat(this.view.amountInput.value);
    const rate = parseFloat(this.view.rateInput.value);
    const term = parseFloat(this.view.termInput.value);
    const monthlyPayment = this.model.calculateMonthlyPayment(amount, rate, term);
    const totalAmount = this.model.calculateTotalAmount(amount, rate, term);
    this.view.updateResult(monthlyPayment, totalAmount);
  }

  onInput() {
    this.view.clearResult();
  }
}
```

Пример кода для создания экземпляра презентера и его инициализации:

```
const view = {
  amountInput: document.getElementById('loanAmount'),
  rateInput: document.getElementById('interestRate'),
  termInput: document.getElementById('loanTerm'),
  resultElement: document.getElementById('result'),

  bindSubmit(callback) {
    const button = document.getElementById('calculateButton');
    button.addEventListener('click', event => {
      event.preventDefault();
      callback();
    });
  },

  bindInput(callback) {
    [this.amountInput, this.rateInput, this.termInput].forEach(input => {
      input.addEventListener('input', callback);
    });
  },

  updateResult(monthlyPayment, totalAmount) {
    this.resultElement.innerHTML = `Ежемесячный платеж: ${monthlyPayment.toFixed(2)} <br> Общая сумма выплат: ${totalAmount.toFixed(2)}`;
  },

  clearResult() {
    this.resultElement.innerHTML = '';
  },
};

const model = new Calculator();
const presenter = new CalculatorPresenter(view, model);
```

